criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Histologically confirmed prostate cancer;

          2. PSA up to 10 ng / ml; Gleason (3 + 3) = 6 (ISUP 1); the stage of the tumor T2a (low-
             risk according to the D'Amico scale);

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Failure of the recording device;

          2. Unsatisfactory audio quality.
